{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setEmails:completion:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"emails"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"emails"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setEmails:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use this for confirmation UI or to chain dependent operations."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import emails from third-party login with confirmation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SocialLoginHandler {","","    func handleGoogleSignIn(_ user: GIDGoogleUser) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        \/\/ Primary email from Google","        if let email = user.profile?.email {","            emails.append(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Additional emails from Google profile if available","        if let additionalEmails = user.profile?.additionalEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: additionalEmails)","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Analytics.track(\"email_sync_failed\", properties: [","                    \"provider\": \"google\",","                    \"email_count\": emails.count,","                    \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                ])","                return","            }","","            Analytics.track(\"email_sync_success\", properties: [","                \"provider\": \"google\",","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            \/\/ Set user ID from Google","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.userID ?? \"\")","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/Pushwoosh